    "This allows individuals to claim that the money is coming from a legitimate source, when in reality it is from an illegal one. 8.",
    "Make use of experts: Money launderers may also make use of experts who have knowledge of legal structures, accounting practices, and tax regulations.",
    "This will help them in creating complex financial transactions that are difficult to trace back to them. 9.",
    "Make use of financial instruments: Money launderers can also make use of financial instruments like wire transfers and foreign exchange transactions to move funds in and out of countries.",
